    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54B32 3.2L inline-six delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring direct mechanical connection. The drivetrain is anchored by the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Significant preventative work has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and subframe reinforcement, mitigating common E46 weak points. The suspension retains its factory composure with refreshed bushings, offering precise turn-in and minimal body roll. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
