    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the slightest signs of careful road use consistent with a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple, the dashboard is free of any cracks or fading, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, and I have maintained a comprehensive folder of service records. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. Whether you are commuting or taking a long-distance trip, this car offers a worry-free experience with many miles of dependable service ahead. It represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer who values a vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
