      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M Variable Differential Lock. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the car's signature 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. While showing minor signs of use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal specimen for the spirited driver seeking a pure analog experience.",
